<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>Rev. Mangdal</author>
<hymn_number>248</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Mim bang pienna nuoi simlei ah,
 Melma dogal siel ang a lien;
 Sanggah keia ding tumin,
 Van nuoi thimpi a zing ie.

[V2]
 Aw van Lal chungnung pen
 Ka limbelh Lal nunnem
 Felna ni vak tuoi lo, Zion Lal
 Ka lampi thim hun salhvak in

[V3]
 2. Lam bang etchim loh ngaih minsel
 Chun leh zuo ngaihpan a sam ie
 Zuomang chung Pathien ang lai,
 Sihsiel ang na zuon ta maw?

[V4]
 3. Ngaih ding dieng, na nung sul ahin
 Sung In giel tui bangin a dai
 Kuongtap la mei a val lo
 Dahluot huiva bang ka mau.

[V5]
 4. Khen lohna chatuon khawpi ah
 Ngilhloh cheng tuoi loin laileng
 Hin tuoilo nawp kipan ding
 Chatuon lal, limbelh ang ah

[V6]
 5. Zingdawng Sawl No suoh ka ngaklah
 Tatsa tui bang luongkhawm ta ding
 Lalpa'n tui bang ei gawp tieng
 Dah cheng sawl ang bang tang ie.

[V7]
 6. Zion kawlni, hung suok mengin
 Melma dogal cheng tawmna di'n
 Salem Lal Thimthu lel tieng
 Lei do cheng dah muolsuok ding.</lyrics>
<title>Ngaih Minsel !</title>
</song>